            "num": "1",
            "text": "God, please save me!"
          },
          {
            "tag": "q2",
            "text": "Yahweh, come quickly to help me!"
          },
          {
            "tag": "v",
            "num": "2",
            "text": "Disgrace those who are happy about my troubles, those who are trying to kill me."
          },
          {
            "tag": "q2",
            "text": "Chase them away; make everyone shame them, for they want to see me suffer."
          },
          {
            "tag": "v",
            "num": "3",
            "text": "I hope that you will cause them to become dismayed and ashamed"
          },
          {
            "tag": "q2",
            "text": "because they have been happy about my troubles."
          },
          {
            "tag": "v",
            "num": "4",
            "text": "But I hope that everyone who prays to you will rejoice because of you."
          },
          {
            "tag": "q2",
            "text": "I hope that everyone who waits for you to rescue them will say,"
          },
          {
            "tag": "q1",
            "text": "\"God is great!\""
          },
          {
            "tag": "v",
            "num": "5",
            "text": "As for me, I am poor and needy;"
